tweets.text:
@FBIIndianapolis announced the 84-year sentence for a Colorado man who sexually exploited more than 84 children and an unknown number of adults from across the United States and five foreign countries. Thirteen of the victims were from Indiana. The defendant also sex trafficked at least five victims. 

Investigators believe additional victims may still be unidentified. If you or someone you know has been a victim of Austin Ryan Lauless, also known online as Cason Fredrickson or APOPHIS, contact your local FBI field office, call 1-800-CALL-FBI, or report it online at https://t.co/tGqFRcJykB.

https://t.co/nnN9TzRoUH

